name: FAAA⅃L
description:
FAAA⅃L is part of "kisetsu".
 This digital painting plays with movement and letters.
 Fall is symbol of introspection and balance, harvest and preparation.
 The Maturity.
 As the golden leaves fall from the trees, we learn to let go, and humbly we keep our memories, leaving behind what’s not necessary.
 What I see is not what everyone sees, look inside yourself, find the meaning.
